text:
Kamilla Serikbay (born 2002) is a Kazakhstani beauty pageant titleholder who was appointed as Miss Universe Kazakhstan 2020 and represented Kazakhstan at Miss Universe 2020.
Serikbay was born in Kyzylorda. She studies at the Suleiman Demirel University with a degree in Applied Law.
Serikbay was appointed as Miss Universe Kazakhstan 2020 and represented Kazakhstan at Miss Universe 2020.
